_:N2e481ae6b53d4b91918ebf6f6773f702 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Peter Kyle was appointed Secretary of State for Business and Trade and President of the Board of Trade on 5 September 2025. He was previously Secretary of State for Science, Innovation and Technology from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Hove and Portslade in July 2024.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
